wiki.summary: LP version released in December 2006 by Agonia Records, limited to 666 copies. Re-released in 2008 by Agonia Records. The new version of Goatcraft Torment includes improved artwork and complete lyrics as the first press was missing some of them. Read more on Last.fm.
